description:
Proper Japanese Title: ミラクルジャンプ

Spin-off of Weekly Young Jump. Initially used sequential numbering and published sporadically, then switched to a regular monthly publishing schedule and used the traditional annual renumbering system. Though it does have its own serials (often only lasting a few chapters), it is mainly a vehicle for one-shots, while also promoting Young Jump franchises that are not serialized in the magazine.

Serializations from this magazine include:

  • D'z
  • Ex-Vita
  • Jasmin
  • Keppeki Danshi! Aoyama-kun
  • Maou-sama Chotto Sore Totte!!
  • Mononogatari
  • Saihate Drive
  • Terra Formars
